s: I first started buying Noanta macrame cord because of the low price. I like the smoothness of the cord although it frays a little too easily for my liking but it is nothing a bit 9of wax or clear nail polish won't fix. I have purchased quite a few spools from them and have recommended it to others who macrame. But, over time, and probably due to its popularity, the price has went up to a point that I am now looking at other brands ...
